  "stem": "<p>In triangle <math><mi>P</mi><mi>Q</mi><mi>R</mi></math>, the measure of angle <math><mi>P</mi></math> is <math><mn>38</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>, the measure of angle <math><mi>Q</mi></math> is <math><mn>90</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>, and the measure of angle <math><mi>R</mi></math> is <math><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mi>k</mi><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo><mo>&#176;</mo></math>. What is the value of <math><mi>k</mi></math>?</p>",
