  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. Angles in a triangle sum to 180\u00b0. So 38 + 90 + k/3 = 180, giving k/3 = 52, so k = 156.</p><p>Choice A is half of k/3. Choice B is k/3, not k. Choice C is k/3\u00b72.</p>",
